      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POP POP BANG (2) got around 390m in a respectable 22.16 when winning a Restricted WIN at this track last start. Rates a top chance again if runs up to latest. DIMORA BIG BOY (4) flew the lids from the middle with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 22.25 when a head winner over 390m at Warrnambool. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Capable of going well again. GOLD HARADA (1) missed the frame last time when fourth (23.86) at Horsham but prior to that had two placings in a row. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Worth another chance. PAW ALLESANDRA (8) is worth including after a top-three finish most recently.",
